{
  "info": {
    "name": "Krypton E-commerce — Reportes / Exportables",
    "description": "Reportes administrativos exportables a Excel (.xlsx) y PDF de Krypton.\n\nTodos los endpoints son SOLO ADMIN (/api/admin/reports) y devuelven un archivo binario como descarga (Content-Disposition: attachment). En Postman usá el botón 'Send and Download' (la flechita al lado de Send) para guardar el archivo y abrirlo.\n\nFlujo sugerido:\n1. Corré 'Login (admin)' → guarda {{adminToken}}.\n2. (Opcional, para el caso 403) Registrá/logueá un cliente → guarda {{clientToken}}.\n3. Ajustá {{desde}} / {{hasta}} (formato ISO yyyy-MM-dd) y {{productId}} a datos que existan.\n4. Disparás cualquiera de los 8 reportes (4 reportes x Excel/PDF).\n\nBase URL por defecto: http://localhost:8080\nAdmin sembrado: admin@krypton.pe / Admin123!\n\n4 reportes:\n- R1 Ventas por período: total facturado (solo órdenes CONFIRMADA), agrupado por día o mes en timezone America/Lima. desde/hasta OBLIGATORIOS, granularidad = dia|mes (default dia).\n- R2 Productos más vendidos: ranking top-N por unidades e ingresos. limit default 10, máx 100. Rango de fechas opcional (ambos o ninguno).\n- R3 Kardex por producto: stock actual + historial de movimientos (ENTRADA/SALIDA). productId OBLIGATORIO (404 si no existe). Rango de fechas opcional.\n- R4 Listado de órdenes: exporta órdenes con filtros opcionales (status, desde, hasta, userId).\n\nNotas de comportamiento:\n- Feature 100% read-only: ninguna escritura, sin migración nueva.\n- Resultado vacío → 200 con un archivo válido (planilla/PDF sin filas de datos), nunca 204.\n- Validación de params → 400 (fecha mal formateada, param requerido ausente, status inválido).\n- Sin token → 401. Token de CLIENTE en endpoint admin → 403.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl",        "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "adminToken",     "value": "" },
    { "key": "clientToken",    "value": "" },
    { "key": "adminEmail",     "value": "admin@krypton.pe" },
    { "key": "adminPassword",  "value": "Admin123!" },
    { "key": "clientEmail",    "value": "cliente@test.pe" },
    { "key": "clientPassword", "value": "Cliente123!" },
    { "key": "productId",      "value": "1" },
    { "key": "desde",          "value": "2026-01-01" },
    { "key": "hasta",          "value": "2026-12-31" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Setup — Tokens",
      "description": "Login de admin (obligatorio para los reportes) y de cliente (solo para el caso 403).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login (admin) → guarda adminToken",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('adminToken', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('adminToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Register (cliente) — para el caso 403",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Cliente Tester\",\n  \"email\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{clientPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "201 si es nuevo, 409 si ya existe (saltá este paso en ese caso)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Login (cliente) → guarda clientToken",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('clientToken', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('clientToken guardado');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{clientEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{clientPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "R1 — Ventas por período",
      "description": "Total facturado de órdenes CONFIRMADA en el rango, agrupado por día/mes (timezone America/Lima). desde y hasta son OBLIGATORIOS. granularidad = dia | mes (default dia).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /ventas/excel",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ventas/excel?desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}&granularidad=dia",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ventas", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}" },
                { "key": "granularidad", "value": "dia", "description": "dia | mes" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Descarga el .xlsx de ventas por período. Usá 'Send and Download'. Cambiá granularidad a 'mes' para el desglose mensual."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /ventas/pdf",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ventas/pdf?desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}&granularidad=mes",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ventas", "pdf"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}" },
                { "key": "granularidad", "value": "mes", "description": "dia | mes" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Descarga el .pdf de ventas por período (acá con granularidad mensual). Usá 'Send and Download'."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "R2 — Productos más vendidos",
      "description": "Ranking top-N por unidades vendidas e ingresos, sobre órdenes CONFIRMADA. limit default 10 (máx 100). Rango de fechas opcional: o pasás desde Y hasta, o ninguno.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /productos-vendidos/excel",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/productos-vendidos/excel?desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "productos-vendidos", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}", "description": "opcional (ambos o ninguno)" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}", "description": "opcional (ambos o ninguno)" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "10", "description": "default 10, máx 100" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Top-N productos a .xlsx. Para el ranking histórico completo, borrá desde y hasta de los query params."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /productos-vendidos/pdf",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/productos-vendidos/pdf?limit=5",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "productos-vendidos", "pdf"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "5", "description": "default 10, máx 100" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Top-5 productos a .pdf, sin filtro de fechas (ranking histórico)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "R3 — Kardex por producto",
      "description": "Stock actual + historial de movimientos (ENTRADA/SALIDA) de UN producto. productId OBLIGATORIO (404 si no existe). Rango de fechas opcional sobre los movimientos.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /kardex/excel",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/kardex/excel?productId={{productId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "kardex", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "productId", "value": "{{productId}}", "description": "obligatorio" },
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Kardex del producto {{productId}} a .xlsx. Habilitá desde/hasta para acotar los movimientos por fecha."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /kardex/pdf",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/kardex/pdf?productId={{productId}}&desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "kardex", "pdf"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "productId", "value": "{{productId}}", "description": "obligatorio" },
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}", "description": "opcional" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}", "description": "opcional" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Kardex del producto {{productId}} a .pdf, acotado por rango de fechas."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "R4 — Listado de órdenes",
      "description": "Exporta órdenes con filtros OPCIONALES: status (PENDIENTE|CONFIRMADA|CANCELADA), desde, hasta, userId. Sin filtros = todas.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /ordenes/excel",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ordenes/excel?status=CONFIRMADA&desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ordenes", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "CONFIRMADA", "description": "opcional: PENDIENTE|CONFIRMADA|CANCELADA" },
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}", "description": "opcional" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}", "description": "opcional" },
                { "key": "userId", "value": "", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Órdenes CONFIRMADA del rango a .xlsx. Borrá los query params para exportar todas."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "GET /ordenes/pdf",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ordenes/pdf",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ordenes", "pdf"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "desde", "value": "", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "userId", "value": "", "description": "opcional", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Todas las órdenes a .pdf, sin filtros. Habilitá los query params para acotar."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Casos de error",
      "description": "Validación de params y guards de autorización.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "400 — ventas sin 'desde' (param requerido ausente)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ventas/excel?hasta={{hasta}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ventas", "excel"],
              "query": [{ "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}" }]
            },
            "description": "Falta el param obligatorio 'desde'. Debe responder 400 (MissingServletRequestParameterException)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "400 — fecha mal formateada",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ventas/excel?desde=01-01-2026&hasta={{hasta}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ventas", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "desde", "value": "01-01-2026", "description": "formato inválido (debe ser yyyy-MM-dd)" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "'desde' no está en ISO yyyy-MM-dd. Debe responder 400 (MethodArgumentTypeMismatchException)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "400 — kardex sin 'productId'",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/kardex/excel",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "kardex", "excel"]
            },
            "description": "Falta el param obligatorio 'productId'. Debe responder 400."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "404 — kardex con productId inexistente",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/kardex/pdf?productId=999999",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "kardex", "pdf"],
              "query": [{ "key": "productId", "value": "999999" }]
            },
            "description": "El producto 999999 no existe. Debe responder 404."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "401 — sin token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ventas/excel?desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ventas", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Sin Authorization header. Debe responder 401."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "403 — cliente accede a reporte admin",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{clientToken}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/reports/ventas/excel?desde={{desde}}&hasta={{hasta}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "reports", "ventas", "excel"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "desde", "value": "{{desde}}" },
                { "key": "hasta", "value": "{{hasta}}" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Token de CLIENTE en endpoint de ADMIN. Debe responder 403 Forbidden."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
